# UC-01.04: De-register Organisation / Deactivate User


sequenceDiagram
    participant OrgAdmin as Organisation Admin
    participant FMAR_UI as FMAR API/UI
    participant ARM as Asset Registration Module
    participant PSQM as Qualification Module
    participant SPUM as SPUM Module
    participant FMARAdmin as FMAR Administrator

    OrgAdmin->>FMAR_UI: Step 1 - Initiate de-registration request
    FMAR_UI->>ARM: Step 2 - Check for active assets
    FMAR_UI->>PSQM: Step 3 - Check for qualified market units
    ARM-->>FMAR_UI: Step 4 - Return asset status
    PSQM-->>FMAR_UI: Step 5 - Return qualification status
    FMAR_UI->>SPUM: Step 6 - Proceed with deactivation
    SPUM-->>FMAR_UI: Step 7 - Mark organisation and users inactive
    FMAR_UI-->>FMARAdmin: Step 8 - Log audit record
